main: ^It is celebrated in Baco, Mindoro as hanksgiving for the abundance of banana in the Municipality of Baco. The festival also features sumptuous meals and delicacies whose main ingredient is banana.

c-0: ^Bananas are displayed on artistically-designed booths made of materials from banana trees. It features the distinctive assortments of banana like the Senorita, the Latundan, the Lacatan and the Saba.
